      *------------*
      *計画予定日*
      *------------*
     C           @KYY      IFLT 1994
     C           @KMM      ORLT 1
     C           @KMM      ORGT 12
     C                     SETON                     0299
     C                     MOVELER,2      MSG
     C                     GOTO STP2
     C                     END
